'''特倫·阿歷山大-阿諾'''（{{lang-en|Trent Alexander-Arnold}}；{{bd|1998年|10月7日}}）是一位[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[足球|足球]]運動員，在場上司職[[後衛|右後衛]]，現在效力於[[英超|英超]]球隊[[利物浦足球俱樂部|利物浦]]，[[英格蘭足球代表隊|英格蘭足球代表隊]]成員。他被認為是現今球壇最出色的右閘之一。

他出身自[[利物浦足球俱樂部|利物浦]]青訓，他在2016年18歲時首次為利物浦一隊上陣，於2017年和2018年均獲選為利物浦球隊最佳年青球員。阿諾曾代表[[英格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U16]]至[[英格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|U21]]國家隊，2018年6月首次出戰成年國家隊，並入選[[2018年世界盃|2018年世界盃]]英格蘭國家隊23人參賽名單。

他的外祖母多琳·卡林曾與前曼聯主練亞歷克斯·弗格森爵士交往，然後搬到紐約市，後來在那裡結婚。 因此，亞歷山大-阿諾德在英格蘭首次亮相之前有資格為美國效力。

==球會生涯==
===利物浦===
====早年====
阿歷山大-阿諾出生在[[利物浦|利物浦]]西德比區（West Derby），就讀聖馬修斯天主教小學<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.mirror.co.uk/sport/football/news/who-trent-alexander-arnold-you-9121409 |title=Who is Trent Alexander-Arnold? All you need to know about Liverpool youngster as he starts at Old Trafford |first=Marcus |last=Hogg |newspaper=每日鏡報 |location=倫敦 |date=2017-01-15|accessdate=11-3-2018 |archive-date=2018-03-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180311001124/https://www.mirror.co.uk/sport/football/news/who-trent-alexander-arnold-you-9121409 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.liverpoolecho.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/liverpools-trent-alexander-arnold-happy-13962453 |title=Why Liverpool's Trent Alexander-Arnold is happy, still dreaming and committed to being a defender |newspaper=利物浦回聲報 |last=Kelly |first=Andy |date=2017-11-28|accessdate=2018-04-18|archive-date=2018-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180418162316/https://www.liverpoolecho.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/liverpools-trent-alexander-arnold-happy-13962453 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

當他六歲時，當地的[[利物浦足球俱樂部|利物浦足球俱樂部]]主辦了一個社區夏令營，他的學校應邀參加了該夏令營。阿歷山大-阿諾被選中參加，利物浦青訓學院的教練伊恩·巴里根（Ian Barrigan）發現他的天份並邀請他加入學院。他開始每週訓練兩到三次，然後在教練[[佩平·利達斯|佩平·利達斯]]的指導下繼續擔任U16和U18級別的球隊隊長<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/44081528 |title=Trent Alexander-Arnold: Liverpool’s local boy on family values & shining on world stage |publisher=BBC體育 |last=Roan |first=Dan |date=11-5-2018 |accessdate=12-5-2018 |archive-date=2018-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180512050020/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/44081528 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.liverpoolfc.com/team/academy/player/trent-alexander-arnold |title=Trent Alexander-Arnold |publisher=利物浦足球俱樂部網站 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170505234440/http://www.liverpoolfc.com/team/academy/player/trent-alexander-arnold |archivedate=2017-05-05|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.liverpoolecho.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/trent-alexander-arnold-liverpool-exclusive-12993256 |title=Trent Alexander-Arnold exclusive – My Liverpool dream came true but I'm only just getting started |first=James |last=Pearce |newspaper=利物浦回聲報 |date=2017-05-05|accessdate=11 -3- 2018 |archive-date=2018-03-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180311001658/https://www.liverpoolecho.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/trent-alexander-arnold-liverpool-exclusive-12993256 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.liverpoolecho.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/liverpool-lijnders-trent-alexander-arnold-13024449 |title=Pep Lijnders Liverpool Q&A – on Trent Alexander-Arnold and the Reds' most important signing |first=James |last=Pearce |newspaper=利物浦回聲報 |date=12 -5- 2017 |accessdate=11 -3- 2018 |archive-date=2018-03-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180311001821/https://www.liverpoolecho.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/liverpool-lijnders-trent-alexander-arnold-13024449 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

他在學院期間表現出色，並在2015年被前利物浦隊長[[謝拉特|謝拉特]]在他的自傳中稱讚阿歷山大-阿諾，稱他將會在利物浦前途無可限量<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.express.co.uk/sport/football/724740/Liverpool-Steven-Gerrard-Jurgen-Klopp-EFL-Cup-Trent-Alexander-Arnold-Premier-League |title=Liverpool prodigy set to make debut against Tottenham after endorsement from Gerrard |first=Paul |last=Joyce |newspaper=Daily Express |location=London |date=2016-10-24|accessdate=11 -3- 2018 |archive-date=2018-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180412114454/https://www.express.co.uk/sport/football/724740/Liverpool-Steven-Gerrard-Jurgen-Klopp-EFL-Cup-Trent-Alexander-Arnold-Premier-League |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。

在2015-16賽季的比賽中，利物浦領隊[[班頓·羅渣士|班頓·羅渣士]]提升阿歷山大-阿諾上一隊，在球隊季前熱身賽首度上陣對陣[[斯温登足球俱乐部|斯温登足球俱乐部]]，比賽以2-1獲勝。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.liverpoolfc.com/fixtures2015/first-team/swindon-v-liverpool-8476/match-centre |title=Match centre: Swindon v Liverpool |publisher=Liverpool F.C. |date=2 -8-2015 |accessdate=2017-03-23|archive-date=2017-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170916060156/http://www.liverpoolfc.com/fixtures2015/first-team/swindon-v-liverpool-8476/match-centre |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.liverpoolecho.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/liverpool-fc-teen-trent-alexander-9776590 |title=Liverpool FC teen Trent Alexander-Arnold: Who the Reds' latest young star is after debut against Swindon |newspaper=利物浦回聲報 |last=Walsh |first=Kristian |date=3 -8- 2015 |accessdate=9 -7-2018 |archive-date=2018-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180709094427/https://www.liverpoolecho.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/liverpool-fc-teen-trent-alexander-9776590 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

====2016年至今====
阿歷山大-阿諾參加了利物浦在美國的季前巡迴賽。他在2016年10月25日首次亮相，在[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]第四輪以2-1戰勝[[熱刺|熱刺]]，該場賽事他在上半場向[[熱刺|熱刺]]後衛[[賓·戴維斯_(1993年生足球員)|-{zh-hans:本·戴维斯;zh-hk:賓·戴維斯}-]]犯規被罰[[黃牌|黃牌]]，常規正選的右後衛[[纳塔涅尔·克莱因|克莱因]]在第68分鐘後備上陣替換阿歷山大-阿諾<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.espn.co.uk/football/liverpool/story/2960077/trent-alexander-arnold-hopeful-of-chance-in-liverpool-first-team |title=Trent Alexander-Arnold hopeful of chance in Liverpool first team |first=Glenn |last=Price |publisher=ESPN |date=2016-09-28|accessdate=11-3-2018 |archive-date=2018-03-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180311002359/http://www.espn.co.uk/football/liverpool/story/2960077/trent-alexander-arnold-hopeful-of-chance-in-liverpool-first-team |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/37686653 |title=Liverpool 2–1 Tottenham Hotspur |first=Luke |last=Reddy |publisher=BBC體育 |date=2016-10-25|accessdate=11-3- 2018 |archive-date=2018-03-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180311002530/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/37686653 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。前利物浦隊長[[謝拉特|謝拉特]]稱讚阿諾首戰的優秀表現，他亦與隊友[[史杜歷治|史杜歷治]]一同被選入聯賽盃第四圈最佳陣容
